Package gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CrewMembersScreen
    A screen to display crew members and to complete actions for each one.
    DailyScoreScreen
    A screen to display the score at the end of every day.
    EndGameScreen
    A screen to display when the game has ended.
    GUIWindow
    A container to put all frames for running the game.
    InstructionsScreen
    An instructions screen to display to help the user play the game.
    MainScreen
    A screen for the user to choose what they would like to do in the game.
    OpeningScreen
    A screen that is shown when the game is first opened.
    PilotShipScreen
    A screen to allow the user to pilot their ship to a new planet.
    SetUpScreen
    A screen for the user to create a game.
    ShipStatusScreen
    A screen to display the status of the ship.
    UseItemScreen
    A screen to make a crew member use an item.
    ViewInventoryScreen
    A screen to view the inventory of the ship.
    ViewShopScreen
    A screen to view and purchase items.
    VisitOutpostScreen
    A screen to either view the shop or the inventory of the ship.
